        </figure>

        <ol marker="a.">
          <li>
            <p>
              Estimate the partial derivative <m>f_x(-2,-1)</m>. (Hint: How can you find values of <m>f</m> that are of the form <m>f(-2+h)</m> and <m>f(-2-h)</m> so that you can use a symmetric difference quotient?)
            </p>
          </li>

